    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_005_000053",
    "sentence": "王薨後，孝昭不豫，見文宣爲祟。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_005_000054",
    "sentence": "孝昭深惡之，厭勝術備設而無益也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_005_000055",
    "sentence": "薨三旬而孝昭崩。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_005_000056",
    "sentence": "大寧二年，葬於武寧之西北，諡閔悼王。",
    "entities": [
